Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases where it leads to a subsequent 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for cases where activity Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to next activity in the process
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Request Payment' in cases where the declaration is eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases ending with 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Payment Handled for cases where activity Payment Handled occurs

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases where the declaration is resubmitted and approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases successfully concluded with 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Payment Handled for cases where activity Payment Handled occurs

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases with multiple rejections
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER for cases where activity Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER occurs

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases where budget owner's approval is required
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' from the start of the process
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
